{"id":"anamim","term":"Anamim","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The name of an Egyptian tribe descended from Mizraim (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 10:13\">Gen. 10:13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:11\">1 Chr. 1:11</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 10:13","1 Chronicles 1:11"]}